item.title: By: Miss
item.dc:creator: Miss
item.description: We share a love for AHS. Jessica Lange is most definitely the "baddest witch in town". My favorite was the coked out Fiona in the hotel room.

item.title: By: Denys
item.dc:creator: Denys
item.description: I want to look like Jessica Lange when I'm her age. She's gorgeous!
item.content:encoded: I want to look like Jessica Lange when I’m her age. She’s gorgeous!

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description: This season has been fantastic! I'll pretty much watch Jessica Lange do anything at this point, but she just keeps getting better every season. Her "I'm in charge everywhere" line is probably my most favorite thing anyone has ever said ever.
